adb shell /data/local/tmp/print_birthday_card Finally, we can run auto-generated tests to ensure the bindings work: interoperability/bindgen/Android.bp : rust_test { name: "libbirthday_bindgen_test", srcs: [":libbirthday_bindgen"], crate_name: "libbirthday_bindgen_test", test_suites: ["general-tests"], auto_gen_config: true, clippy_lints: "none", // Generated file, skip linting lints: "none",
} atest libbirthday_bindgen_test

